name: Australia NFT
description: NFTcountry Australia. The base is made of precious Australian opal. Top pillar in solid gold and opal in the shape of the famous Sydney Opera House, with ruby windows. Rotates around the edges with the "Diamonds" mechanism. The lower part of the stand is made of white marble. A distinctive feature of the figurine is the Kangaroo (Symbol of Australia), which moves in a circle with the help of the Clockwork Mechanism. On the back of the emblem of the Sydney Opera House.
